Abstrak: The article reviews the ceramic art exhibition "Rose Cabat: 100 Years," which featured works by the late ceramic artist Rose Cabat at the Couturier Gallery in Los Angeles, California from May 17 to July 5, 2014.
Sumber: Ceramics: Art & Perception. Dec2015-Jan2016, Issue 102, p68-71. 4p. 7 Color Photographs
